info.author: John Troony
info.description:
This is the “irc_con.py" module, and it provides one function called
irc_connect (server, channel, nick ) which connects to an irc server, 
then a channel with nick as parsed.
info.name: irc_con
info.summary: A simple IRC connector(No support for SSL/ident)
